CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

September 15, 2008

[Cite as 09/1512008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-4613.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2005-1531. Disciplinary Counsel v. Quatman.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing on July 14, 2008, by relator, Disciplinary Counsel, of a motion to lift stayed suspension and impose a one-year actual suspension from the practice of law. Respondent filed a memo in opposition to the motion. Upon consideration thereof,

*1456It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.

Moyer, C.J., and O’Connor, J., dissent and would grant the motion. Cupp, J., not participating.
